<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[الشِّحْر]</span>: ساحل البحر بين اليمن وعُمان، قال العجاج <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رحلتُ من أقصى بلاد الرِّحَلِ <span class="c2">«٢»</span> ... من قُللِ الشِّحْر فَجَنْبَيْ مَوْكَلِ <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فِعْلَة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[ن]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[الشِّحْنة]</span>: العداوة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
